{"tid":1562634,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"事實係我地未贏, 香港人權法未通過","createTime":"2019-09-12T05:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T14:21:33.000Z","uid":69291,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"5962921262c9e8e5da09dfe49e7bfac60fffe3a8","tid":1562634,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:42:04.000Z","msg":"我知會有人屌我失敗主義<br />\n負評,block<br />\n但我都係要講<br />\n<br />\n事實係人權法仲未通過<br />\n什至幾時傾都好似未知<br />\n中共港共反應好大<br />\n通過與否依然有暗涌<br />\n大國間既政治, 半日都嫌多<br />\n我只係知道法案一日未通過, 我地都唔安全<br />\n所有手足都繼續有被虐打既風險<br />\n<br />\n事實係我地仲未獲得勝利<br />\n三個幾月, 五大訴求只係達成一個<br />\n但我地付出既代價無比巨大<br />\n然後尋日佢哋仲串柒柒話想推蒙面法<br />\n無放過各位在眼內<br />\n<br />\n事實係我地仲有好漫長既戰鬥<br />\n自己香港自己救<br />\n有外力支援當然最好<br />\n但我地本土既戰線都要做好<br />\n行動post, 文宣方向<br />\n英領集會？<br />\n德領集會？<br />\n美領再集會？<br />\n913和你拖？<br />\n914天水圍？<br />\n915銅鑼灣？<br />\n<br />\n我明白大家都好攰<br />\n我都唔反對有首歌可以振奮士氣<br />\n我只希望大家唱完歌之後要繼續緊守我地既信念<br />\n咬實牙關, 繼續為自由, 為民主, 為香港奮鬥<br />\n直到真正重光一刻<br />\n<br />\n最後多謝你睇到呢到,<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n九一五<br />\n銅鑼灣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8TNf7fi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8TNf7fi.jpg&h=0fc351d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uPoGim9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuPoGim9.jpg&h=8d11a08b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qkdZPtP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqkdZPtP.jpg&h=3bdcb696&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df628b3ca39bb665124a213d3c5a4597c281aeee","tid":1562634,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f09a0